reviewText:
There is is one stinker.  The other two are good but the image quality makes it harder to enjoy.

Men in War-great story/great image quality(gem).

Cry of Battle-great story/great image quality(gem).

Fort Algiers-poor story/good image quality(the stinker imho).

The Tiger and the Flame-good story/poor image quality(1st bollywood film?)

Crooked Way-great story/great image quality(gem).

Code 7 Vcitim 5-good story/poor image quality.
